Warning! Sedation, lethargy,
difficulty thinking,

170
00:15:18,618 --> 00:15:22,353
memory loss, nightmares,

171
00:15:22,355 --> 00:15:25,924
Manic feelings, delusions,
seizures, and death.

172
00:15:27,526 --> 00:15:29,093
Well, it's prescribed.

173
