I always do that.

177
00:15:45,711 --> 00:15:48,212
Ow!
[Phone rings]

178
00:15:51,984 --> 00:15:54,986
[phone ringing]

179
00:15:54,988 --> 00:16:00,692
<i>[strange voices]</i>
<i>No! Daddy!</i>

180
00:16:00,694 --> 00:16:02,393
[Phone ringing]

181
00:16:05,731 --> 00:16:07,665
[phone ringing]

182
