Hello?
<i>(Jason) Lizzy?</i>

183
00:16:16,109 --> 00:16:18,109
<i>Is everything okay?</i>

184
00:16:18,111 --> 00:16:19,978
<i>I've been trying to call you for half an hour.</i>

185
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:22,146
A half an hour?
What are you talking about?

186
00:16:22,148 --> 00:16:24,649
<i>I've been calling your cell phone and the house phone.</i>

187
00:16:24,651 --> 00:16:26,317
<i>What, you</i>
<i>can't hear it?</i>

188
00:16:26,319 --> 00:16:29,454
No, I was in the bathroom

189
00:16:29,456 --> 00:16:33,524
and I shattered
my glass everywhere.

190
00:16:33,526 --> 00:16:36,894
<i>You sound funny.</i>
<i>Are you okay?</i>

191
00:16:36,896 --> 00:16:41,265
No. No, I'm fine.
I'm fine.

192
00:16:41,267 --> 00:16:43,735
Just I'm feeling a little out of it is all.

193
00:16:43,737 --> 00:16:47,605
<i>Look, just run a bath and I'll be-- [busy signal]</i>

194
00:16:47,607 --> 00:16:49,540
Hello?

195
00:16:49,542 --> 00:16:53,678
Jason. Jas--
[loud squealing sound]

196
00:16:53,680 --> 00:16:57,081
[dialing phone]

197
00:16:57,083 --> 00:17:01,019
<i>"We're sorry.</i>
<i>Your call cannot be completed as dialed."</i>

198
00:17:01,021 --> 00:17:03,488
<i>"Please check the number</i>
<i>and dial again."</i>

199
00:17:03,490 --> 00:17:06,024
[Dialing]

200
00:17:08,027 --> 00:17:09,961
[beep]

201
