you're feeling better.

207
00:18:27,440 --> 00:18:29,340
I am feeling better.

208
00:18:29,342 --> 00:18:31,876
I took a really long nap,
and I just relaxed.

209
00:18:31,878 --> 00:18:33,344
That's great.

210
00:18:33,346 --> 00:18:35,046
So tell me you got
the wine.

211
00:18:35,048 --> 00:18:36,514
What are you
talking about?

212
00:18:36,516 --> 00:18:38,382
Baby, please tell me
you got wine.

213
00:18:38,384 --> 00:18:41,752
Yes, of course I got the wine.
Yes! Thank you.

214
00:18:41,754 --> 00:18:43,788
So I made a couple
phone calls today,

215
00:18:43,790 --> 00:18:46,891
and it looks like I'm going to be tutoring next week.

216
00:18:46,893 --> 00:18:49,594
That's great.

217
00:18:49,596 --> 00:18:51,629
How do you open
this fucking thing?

218
00:18:51,631 --> 00:18:53,464
You know, for all
the wine you drink,

219
00:18:53,466 --> 00:18:55,299
