how to use a corkscrew.

220
00:18:55,301 --> 00:18:56,901
Just be patient.
It will--

221
00:18:56,903 --> 00:19:00,471
Baby. Baby, can you
please open it for me?

222
00:19:00,473 --> 00:19:02,707
Let me
get this straight.

223
00:19:02,709 --> 00:19:06,811
I'm an overworked man out in
the sun all day pouring concrete

224
00:19:06,813 --> 00:19:09,046
and cutting 2X4s.

225
00:19:09,048 --> 00:19:13,351
And I'm making you dinner and you
want me to open this fucking thing?

226
00:19:13,353 --> 00:19:17,755
Yes, I do.
Thank you.

227
00:19:17,757 --> 00:19:20,791
So it looks like it's not going to be a lot of money, but...

228
00:19:20,793 --> 00:19:23,394
I think it's going to get me out of the house for awhile.

229
00:19:23,396 --> 00:19:27,832
Well, if you're happy,
I'm happy.

230
00:19:34,339 --> 00:19:36,374
That's really good.

231
